### 1. Agent Connect (WebSocket)
# Requires REST Client with WS support (e.g. VS Code REST Client)
# Note: Use valid name/token from your database
WEBSOCKET ws://localhost:54321/ws?name=test-agent&token=secret-token

### 2. Send Deployment Finished (WebSocket)
WEBSOCKET ws://localhost:54321/ws-deployment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": "DeploymentFinished",
  "command": {
    "id": "INSERT-UUID-HERE",
    "hasSucceeded": true
  }
}

### 3. Stream Logs (WebSocket)
WEBSOCKET ws://localhost:54321/api/v1/deploy/log/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "line": "Successfully activated the deployment."
}
